01:13:28,110 --> 01:13:33,230
[What does Seo Won's answer mean?]

1308
01:13:35,280 --> 01:13:38,140
I want to ask Gyu Ri.

1309
01:13:38,140 --> 01:13:41,580
How likely is it
that your number one changes?

1310
01:13:41,580 --> 01:13:43,690
Good job. Good question.

1311
01:13:44,730 --> 01:13:46,750
How likely?

1312
01:13:53,600 --> 01:13:58,400
First of all, I won't stop
anyone who comes my way.

1313
01:13:59,740 --> 01:14:01,670
I like straightforward men.

1314
01:14:01,670 --> 01:14:03,660
I won't stop anyone who comes my way.

1315
01:14:03,660 --> 01:14:07,600
And I think that greatly affects my feelings.

1316
01:14:07,600 --> 01:14:13,410
At the end of the day, I can't help being
myself, even in this environment.

1317
01:14:13,410 --> 01:14:18,360
I always liked men
who approach and pursue me.

1318
01:14:18,360 --> 01:14:26,090
So, if there happens to
be someone like that here,

1319
01:14:26,090 --> 01:14:28,110
I think my feelings could change.

1320
01:14:28,110 --> 01:14:30,860
So, I can't really say how likely it is.

1321
01:14:30,860 --> 01:14:35,420
- Whoa, that's her answer?
- She's telling them to approach her.

1322
01:14:38,370 --> 01:14:41,430
Can I ask a follow-up question?

1323
01:14:41,430 --> 01:14:42,900
No.

1324
01:14:43,960 --> 01:14:47,780
- It's not allowed.
- But you did earlier.

1325
01:14:49,160 --> 01:14:51,720
- Why are you doing this?
- Nope.

1326
01:14:53,770 --> 01:14:57,890
- It's hot. It was cold earlier.
- Good thing you opened it.

1327
01:14:57,890 --> 01:15:02,800
[Gyu Ri's turn to ask a question]

1328
01:15:04,730 --> 01:15:07,180
- Wu Yeol.
- Whoa, daebak!

1329
01:15:07,860 --> 01:15:09,800
I'll ask Wu Yeol.

1330
01:15:17,790 --> 01:15:19,420
[Bothered]

1331
01:15:30,720 --> 01:15:41,000
Do you think your feelings or interests
could change after tonight?

1332
01:15:42,720 --> 01:15:44,450
Toward who?

1333
01:15:52,810 --> 01:15:55,250
She looked at Yu Gyeong just now.

1334
01:15:56,100 --> 01:16:00,430
- Interest in...
- Whoever you're thinking of right now.

1335
01:16:00,430 --> 01:16:02,370
I think I'll remain the same.

1336
01:16:02,370 --> 01:16:04,080
He gave her a straight answer.

1337
01:16:04,080 --> 01:16:05,880
[Nods]

1338
01:16:11,350 --> 01:16:14,960
[What was the meaning behind that question?]

1339
01:16:14,960 --> 01:16:18,450
Do you think Yu Gyeong understands
what's going on right now?

1340
01:16:30,710 --> 01:16:34,470
Even if I return to the first day,
I wouldn't change anything.

1341
01:16:34,470 --> 01:16:38,860
My feelings will remain the same.

1342
01:16:43,550 --> 01:16:45,360
Sorry, but I'll grab another bottle of wine.

1343
01:16:45,360 --> 01:16:46,850
We finished this one.

1344
01:16:57,070 --> 01:17:00,620
I wonder how Seo Won feels
after hearing that.

1345
01:17:00,620 --> 01:17:03,770
Did I understand her question correctly?

1346
01:17:03,770 --> 01:17:05,840
[Nods]

1347
01:17:06,480 --> 01:17:09,810
I wish the question were more specific.

1348
01:17:10,980 --> 01:17:12,720
If the question is vague,

1349
01:17:12,720 --> 01:17:15,390
I'll probably give a vague answer as well.

1350
01:17:15,390 --> 01:17:17,030
Then, ask a specific question.

1351
01:17:17,030 --> 01:17:19,370
- I plan to.
- Oh, no!

1352
01:17:28,190 --> 01:17:31,870
[A night when touchy feelings
begin to surface]

1353
01:17:32,440 --> 01:17:35,010
I want to ask Seong Min.

1354
01:17:35,010 --> 01:17:37,190
I'm curious who your top two were.

1355
01:17:37,190 --> 01:17:39,760
- Yu Gyeong and Min Ju?
- Easy.

1356
01:17:43,000 --> 01:17:45,290
I'll ask Yu Gyeong. Who are your top two?

1357
01:17:49,980 --> 01:17:52,550
Wu Yeol and...

1358
01:17:53,540 --> 01:17:55,290
Jun Hyeon.

1359
01:17:55,290 --> 01:17:56,980
Oh, Jun Hyeon!

1360
01:17:57,730 --> 01:18:00,910
- Seong Min!
- What is he eating right now?

1361
01:18:00,910 --> 01:18:05,360
[Such an unfortunate situation]

1362
01:18:05,360 --> 01:18:07,360
Let's go, Min Ju!

1363
01:18:07,360 --> 01:18:09,780
Look at Seong Min's expression!

1364
01:18:09,780 --> 01:18:11,550
Jun Hyeon.

1365
01:18:21,780 --> 01:18:23,990
Look at Min Ju's expression!

1366
01:18:33,340 --> 01:18:35,360
I'll ask Yu Gyeong.

1367
01:18:35,360 --> 01:18:37,580
Was I ever in your top two?

1368
01:18:37,580 --> 01:18:38,980
Yes.

1369
01:18:40,090 --> 01:18:41,790
Why not now?

1370
01:18:41,790 --> 01:18:44,300
- What's wrong with you?
- What are you saying?

1371
01:18:44,300 --> 01:18:46,500
I'm questioning her right now.

1372
01:18:46,500 --> 01:18:49,810
Could your feelings still change-

1373
01:18:49,810 --> 01:18:52,550
Is there still room in your heart?

1374
01:18:59,080 --> 01:19:01,250
I'm not sure.

1375
01:19:05,110 --> 01:19:07,370
- I'll ask Seong Min.
- You, go!

1376
01:19:07,370 --> 01:19:09,740
It's a whirlwind today!

1377
01:19:09,740 --> 01:19:11,290
Go ahead. I'm ready.

1378
01:19:11,290 --> 01:19:14,890
What factors do you consider
when choosing whom to text?

1379
01:19:14,890 --> 01:19:16,890
My first choice.

1380
01:19:19,880 --> 01:19:23,000
Were there purely excitement
and romantic interest,

1381
01:19:23,000 --> 01:19:26,600
or was there also a bit of guilt
and sympathy mixed in?

1382
01:19:27,340 --> 01:19:29,990
Honestly, I was very confused.

1383
01:19:29,990 --> 01:19:31,620
Everything is laid on the table now!

1384
01:19:31,620 --> 01:19:34,880
- Everyone is putting it out there.
- After we went on the date,

1385
01:19:34,880 --> 01:19:36,780
my feelings changed.

1386
01:19:36,780 --> 01:19:39,930
The situation itself was exciting

1387
01:19:39,930 --> 01:19:46,480
and riding the bicycles together
was romantic.

1388
01:19:46,480 --> 01:19:49,940
When we were walking around
outside for a long time,

1389
01:19:49,940 --> 01:19:52,170
it was really cold.

1390
01:19:52,170 --> 01:19:54,190
I was naturally worried.

1391
01:19:54,970 --> 01:19:56,920
But that's different from feeling guilty.

1392
01:19:56,920 --> 01:19:59,970
It means I genuinely care
and think about the person.

1393
01:20:00,690 --> 01:20:05,330
That's what I realized.

1394
01:20:05,330 --> 01:20:08,120
Okay. I completely understand now.

1395
01:20:11,350 --> 01:20:12,470
[Smiles]

1396
01:20:14,490 --> 01:20:16,820
Hyung, did you reveal your top two?

1397
01:20:20,400 --> 01:20:23,610
There was only one person the whole time.

1398
01:20:23,610 --> 01:20:25,610
It was Yu Gyeong.

1399
01:20:26,690 --> 01:20:29,640
- One person all this time!
- So cool.

1400
01:20:31,960 --> 01:20:33,510
[Glances]

1401
01:20:36,120 --> 01:20:37,960
Can I ask Gyu Ri a question?

1402
01:20:37,960 --> 01:20:39,460
- Go ahead.
- Let's go.

1403
01:20:39,460 --> 01:20:43,170
Besides the top two you mentioned earlier,

1404
01:20:43,170 --> 01:20:47,250
if someone else pursued you directly,
would you be open to it?

1405
01:20:47,250 --> 01:20:48,560
Yes.

1406
01:20:49,630 --> 01:20:51,380
- What?
- They all do.

1407
01:21:05,980 --> 01:21:07,390
Let me ask Gyu Ri.

1408
01:21:07,390 --> 01:21:09,610
- Yes, yes!
- Please!

1409
01:21:09,610 --> 01:21:13,750
If your top two choices add up to 100%,

1410
01:21:13,750 --> 01:21:17,000
what percentages are your number one and two?

1411
01:21:33,920 --> 01:21:36,370
Right now...

1412
01:21:36,370 --> 01:21:40,640
my number one is probably around 70-80%.

1413
01:21:49,480 --> 01:21:55,190
But the remaining 20-30%
doesn't belong to number two.

1414
01:21:55,190 --> 01:21:57,910
My top choice is pretty clear at the moment,

1415
01:21:58,900 --> 01:22:04,510
but I haven't seen what the others are like
when they're actively pursuing me.

1416
01:22:06,140 --> 01:22:07,950
That's how I feel.

1417
01:22:08,970 --> 01:22:12,690
My top choice is pretty clear at this point.

1418
01:22:21,990 --> 01:22:24,810
I also want to ask Gyu Ri something.

1419
01:22:30,830 --> 01:22:33,590
You remember that text you sent me?

1420
01:22:34,620 --> 01:22:37,010
- The one under your nickname?
- Yeah.

1421
01:22:39,290 --> 01:22:41,630
What was your intention?

1422
01:22:41,630 --> 01:22:44,170
You said 70-80%,

1423
01:22:45,130 --> 01:22:48,850
so you could've sent the text to that person.

1424
01:22:50,780 --> 01:22:53,300
He's going all out!

1425
01:23:08,640 --> 01:23:11,860
Is 70-80% that significant?

1426
01:23:19,910 --> 01:23:22,650
That's my biggest question.

1427
01:23:24,510 --> 01:23:26,990
Feelings can change.

1428
01:23:26,990 --> 01:23:36,080
That's why I had texted you in the beginning.

1429
01:23:36,080 --> 01:23:39,860
I had a lot I wanted to ask you.

1430
01:23:39,860 --> 01:23:44,570
You said you can get a sense
after three meetings.

1431
01:23:44,570 --> 01:23:47,100
- That's your reason?
- Yes.

1432
01:23:48,420 --> 01:23:50,130
You're curious about me?

1433
01:23:50,130 --> 01:23:52,820
- Yes!
- What's going on?

1434
01:23:53,760 --> 01:23:55,640
Yeah?

1435
01:23:55,640 --> 01:23:59,010
What's going on? What's happening?

1436
01:24:10,550 --> 01:24:13,830
What in the world is going on?

1437
01:24:23,770 --> 01:24:27,610
Let me turn your question back on you.
Is 70-80% insignificant?

1438
01:24:30,030 --> 01:24:32,100
You asked if it was significant.

1439
01:24:33,900 --> 01:24:35,740
- 70-80%?
- Yeah.

1440
01:24:36,930 --> 01:24:39,860
- I feel it's quite significant.
- Currently, it's not insignificant.

1441
01:24:39,860 --> 01:24:42,180
- What is she saying?
- It's still first place.

1442
01:24:42,180 --> 01:24:44,540
It's not insignificant now?

1443
01:24:45,510 --> 01:24:47,230
What I'm saying is...

1444
01:24:48,220 --> 01:24:54,500
if someone were to approach me
because they really liked me

1445
01:24:57,760 --> 01:25:01,750
and they were certain about their feelings,

1446
01:25:11,480 --> 01:25:13,140
then...

1447
01:25:15,440 --> 01:25:20,210
that percentage could be flipped.

1448
01:25:20,940 --> 01:25:25,090
It wouldn't be that hard

1449
01:25:27,000 --> 01:25:33,700
to flip that percentage. I guess.

1450
01:25:46,510 --> 01:25:48,090
Let me ask Wu Yeol.

1451
01:25:48,090 --> 01:25:51,570
Wu Yeol, what's been
on your mind the most lately?

1452
01:25:51,570 --> 01:25:53,980
What has been causing you stress?

1453
01:25:54,800 --> 01:25:56,670
What will he say?

1454
01:26:05,030 --> 01:26:06,880
My top two...

1455
01:26:09,170 --> 01:26:13,120
I can't help but be aware
of those two people.

1456
01:26:16,910 --> 01:26:18,860
Honestly speaking,

1457
01:26:20,010 --> 01:26:24,200
ever since I first arrived,

1458
01:26:24,200 --> 01:26:29,100
my feelings kept...

1459
01:26:31,100 --> 01:26:33,190
wavering between the two.

1460
01:26:34,220 --> 01:26:35,930
Yu Gyeong, too.

1461
01:26:39,630 --> 01:26:43,360
As I spent more time with Yu Gyeong,

1462
01:26:43,360 --> 01:26:45,360
I started having an interest.

1463
01:26:45,360 --> 01:26:48,620
It's true that I developed feelings for her.

1464
01:26:50,030 --> 01:26:51,860
Oh, my gosh!

1465
01:26:51,860 --> 01:26:53,640
He's the most manly.

1466
01:26:53,640 --> 01:26:54,860
[Covering his mouth]

1467
01:26:54,860 --> 01:26:57,980
He's straight to the point.

1468
01:27:11,470 --> 01:27:15,350
But it's not like...

1469
01:27:18,950 --> 01:27:23,380
I didn't have feelings for Gyu Ri.

1470
01:27:26,430 --> 01:27:29,780
I felt that I couldn't justify it to myself

1471
01:27:29,780 --> 01:27:32,970
if I just left...

1472
01:27:32,970 --> 01:27:37,510
without giving her a chance.

1473
01:27:41,840 --> 01:27:46,890
I told Gyu Ri before that I can
get a sense after three meetings.

1474
01:27:55,150 --> 01:27:57,250
I wanted to be honest with her.

1475
01:27:58,010 --> 01:28:01,350
But throughout our conversations,

1476
01:28:01,350 --> 01:28:06,400
there were aspects of Gyu Ri
I couldn't make sense of.

1477
01:28:10,690 --> 01:28:12,950
Anyway, putting all that aside,

1478
01:28:12,950 --> 01:28:16,500
I felt it was right to be straight with her.

1479
01:28:30,690 --> 01:28:36,310
Until this point, the truth games
had all been played by novices.

1480
01:28:36,310 --> 01:28:38,410
This is what you call a truth game.

1481
01:28:38,410 --> 01:28:41,080
Many ended up
revealing their honest feelings.

1482
01:28:41,080 --> 01:28:45,240
They were a mix of facts
and underlying intentions.

1483
01:28:45,240 --> 01:28:47,950
In the process, some people swayed others.

1484
01:28:47,950 --> 01:28:50,000
What I still want to know is,

1485
01:28:50,000 --> 01:28:53,890
Gyu Ri said she likes Seo Won 70-80%.

1486
01:28:53,890 --> 01:28:55,650
But that wasn't true, right?

1487
01:28:55,650 --> 01:28:58,240
- No one knows how she truly feels.
- But it was true.

1488
01:28:58,240 --> 01:29:03,630
That's why she asked if 70-80%
was significant when Wu Yeol asked.

1489
01:29:03,630 --> 01:29:05,540
But Seo Won countered her question

1490
01:29:05,540 --> 01:29:09,200
and asked if her 70-80%
was insignificant, then.

1491
01:29:09,200 --> 01:29:10,390
It became complicated.

1492
01:29:10,390 --> 01:29:14,380
Who Gyu Ri's first choice isn't important.

1493
01:29:14,380 --> 01:29:16,450
Her first choice makes up 70-80%,

1494
01:29:16,450 --> 01:29:19,250
but she made it so anyone could be.

1495
01:29:19,250 --> 01:29:22,240
Nonetheless, Gyu Ri spoke
with an underlying intention.

1496
01:29:22,240 --> 01:29:27,300
Anyway, it was a chance for her to
be honest in front of everyone.

1497
01:29:27,300 --> 01:29:29,270
- Her top two
- Exactly.

1498
01:29:29,270 --> 01:29:31,210
were Seo Won and Jun Hyeon.

1499
01:29:31,210 --> 01:29:35,870
If she had mentioned the 70-80%
after revealing they're not her top two now,

1500
01:29:35,870 --> 01:29:40,210
people would've just wondered
who her top two are and moved on.

1501
01:29:40,210 --> 01:29:42,280
But she got caught in her own trap.

1502
01:29:42,280 --> 01:29:45,840
She didn't want to lose any of them.
Jun Hyeon, Wu Yeol...

1503
01:29:45,840 --> 01:29:48,180
This is legendary.

1504
01:29:48,180 --> 01:29:51,480
They're like lost stars.

1505
01:29:51,480 --> 01:29:53,510
Telling the truth is hard.

1506
01:29:53,510 --> 01:29:55,080
- She's right.
- What is this?

1507
01:29:55,080 --> 01:29:58,860
[The truth game hit like a storm]

1508
01:30:02,160 --> 01:30:03,680
Red wine.

1509
01:30:04,710 --> 01:30:07,310
They must be drinking after the game ended.

1510
01:30:13,590 --> 01:30:15,230
You guys drink so well.

1511
01:30:15,230 --> 01:30:17,160
No, I just really need a drink.

1512
01:30:17,160 --> 01:30:19,570
My tolerance increased.

1513
01:30:19,570 --> 01:30:23,870
- I drank this much!
- Why did you drink so much? Don't.

1514
01:30:23,870 --> 01:30:25,550
You should stop.

1515
01:30:26,990 --> 01:30:28,710
You should stop.

1516
01:30:40,710 --> 01:30:42,920
Who are you messaging, Wu Yeol?

1517
01:30:42,920 --> 01:30:44,660
Why is she asking?

1518
01:30:45,730 --> 01:30:48,560
- My older sister.
- You have a sister?

1519
01:30:48,560 --> 01:30:50,500
How many years apart?

1520
01:30:50,500 --> 01:30:52,350
Same age as Min Ju.

1521
01:30:53,360 --> 01:30:54,300
[Bothered]

1522
01:30:54,870 --> 01:30:56,380
Won!

1523
01:30:57,290 --> 01:30:59,190
[Pouts]

1524
01:30:59,190 --> 01:31:01,600
- Where's the minced garlic?
- Should be there.

1525
01:31:01,600 --> 01:31:03,710
She's nice to him
when it's just the two of them.

1526
01:31:03,710 --> 01:31:05,090
Here it is.

1527
01:31:09,420 --> 01:31:11,870
- Rough night?
- Yeah.

1528
01:31:13,490 --> 01:31:15,730
Today was so rough.

1529
01:31:15,730 --> 01:31:17,450
Really?

1530
01:31:19,910 --> 01:31:20,870
[Sighs]

1531
01:31:20,870 --> 01:31:23,090
What a complete mess.

1532
01:31:31,030 --> 01:31:33,030
[Meanwhile, four people remain
in the living room]

1533
01:31:37,650 --> 01:31:39,230
[Sighs]

1534
01:31:40,450 --> 01:31:41,340
[Glances]

1535
01:31:41,340 --> 01:31:42,250
[Glances]

1536
01:31:49,990 --> 01:31:52,380
If I add to the conversation,

1537
01:31:52,380 --> 01:31:54,670
it'll probably stress you out, right?

1538
01:31:54,670 --> 01:31:58,790
No, at this point, we might as well

1539
01:31:58,790 --> 01:32:01,650
just ask everything...

1540
01:32:01,650 --> 01:32:04,450
- and be honest.
- Truly?

1541
01:32:06,760 --> 01:32:10,370
- I want to know the reason.
- Good question.

1542
01:32:10,370 --> 01:32:12,780
Whether it was our official date,

1543
01:32:12,780 --> 01:32:16,860
giving you a ride in the morning,

1544
01:32:16,860 --> 01:32:20,300
or watching a movie together on Sunday,

1545
01:32:20,300 --> 01:32:25,730
I really enjoyed the time I spent with you.

1546
01:32:25,730 --> 01:32:28,700
There were many moments
when my heart fluttered.

1547
01:32:28,700 --> 01:32:33,600
Whenever I was with you, I always felt
comfortable, had fun, and laughed a lot.

1548
01:32:35,610 --> 01:32:40,110
But honestly, from the moment we first met,

1549
01:32:40,110 --> 01:32:44,900
- I never completely ruled Gyu Ri out.
- That's understandable.

1550
01:32:45,860 --> 01:32:48,080
That's why I said that earlier.

1551
01:32:49,680 --> 01:32:52,080
But of course, it bothered me.

1552
01:32:52,740 --> 01:32:54,990
You were always on my mind.

1553
01:32:55,690 --> 01:32:58,370
I don't feel offended.

1554
01:32:58,370 --> 01:32:59,730
But it did bother me.

1555
01:32:59,730 --> 01:33:02,210
Yes, that's understandable.

1556
01:33:04,140 --> 01:33:09,110
I told Gyu Ri before that I can get
a sense after three meetings.

1557
01:33:18,370 --> 01:33:20,070
You did.

1558
01:33:20,070 --> 01:33:23,510
I should have...

1559
01:33:26,850 --> 01:33:29,750
left no room for misunderstanding.

1560
01:33:33,460 --> 01:33:36,360
We're all doing our best.

1561
01:33:36,360 --> 01:33:39,100
So, we have no regrets.

1562
01:33:39,100 --> 01:33:41,020
That's not the case for me.

1563
01:33:41,020 --> 01:33:43,860
This situation was just...

1564
01:33:47,230 --> 01:33:49,560
Sure, but...

1565
01:33:53,030 --> 01:33:55,810
I'll do my best to understand you.

1566
01:34:00,150 --> 01:34:01,650
[What percentage am I to you, Seo Won?]

1567
01:34:01,650 --> 01:34:03,810
[Whatever the result may be,
I'll take you out to dinner]

1568
01:34:21,030 --> 01:34:23,210
I have something to tell you,
so come to the tea room.

1569
01:34:23,210 --> 01:34:25,330
Oh, my God.

1570
01:34:26,400 --> 01:34:28,670
I'll show you my manly side today.

1571
01:34:31,960 --> 01:34:32,770
[Good night]

1572
01:34:32,770 --> 01:34:35,560
- What the heck?
- She waved to Wu Yeol?

1573
01:34:35,560 --> 01:34:37,160
Hurry up.

1574
01:34:40,220 --> 01:34:41,840
Just like Friday.

1575
01:34:41,840 --> 01:34:43,770
I deliberately sat on the opposite side.

1576
01:34:43,770 --> 01:34:45,780
You've developed a trauma.

1577
01:34:47,080 --> 01:34:50,390
He deliberately sat on the opposite side!

1578
01:34:51,590 --> 01:34:53,050
[Bites her lip]

1579
01:35:06,170 --> 01:35:11,120
[Did you detect their heart signals?]

1580
01:35:11,120 --> 01:35:13,180
[The third official date begins now]

1581
01:35:13,180 --> 01:35:16,430
[Predict who the eight people
choose as their date]

1582
01:35:16,430 --> 01:35:18,110
Okay, let's go. Let's figure this out.

1583
01:35:18,110 --> 01:35:21,780
Tonight, the tenants got texts,
instructed to directly ask

1584
01:35:21,780 --> 01:35:24,510
the person they'd like to go on a date with.

1585
01:35:24,510 --> 01:35:27,360
Today's challenge is to predict the outcome

1586
01:35:27,360 --> 01:35:30,140
of the date requests instead of the texts.

1587
01:35:30,140 --> 01:35:33,770
- Wasn't today too chaotic, though?
- I know.

1588
01:35:33,770 --> 01:35:36,120
In this situation?

1589
01:35:36,120 --> 01:35:38,590
I can't imagine it.

1590
01:35:38,590 --> 01:35:40,500
Shall we start with a sure bet?

1591
01:35:40,500 --> 01:35:42,630
That would be Min Ju, right?

1592
01:35:42,630 --> 01:35:46,260
Rather, Seong Min's feelings for
Yu Gyeong are more certain.

1593
01:35:46,260 --> 01:35:47,730
He did his best to find out.

1594
01:35:47,730 --> 01:35:50,090
If there's still room in your heart.

1595
01:35:50,090 --> 01:35:52,210
I'm not sure.

1596
01:35:52,210 --> 01:35:54,270
Gosh, I can't...

1597
01:35:54,270 --> 01:35:56,760
There aren't many people
who can do what he did.

1598
01:35:56,760 --> 01:35:59,920
They gently back off or just give up,

1599
01:35:59,920 --> 01:36:02,230
but he asked if her heart had room for him.

1600
01:36:02,230 --> 01:36:05,190
- The ultimate devotion, huh?
- This is a no-brainer.

1601
01:36:05,190 --> 01:36:07,480
- Start with Seong Min.
- Seong Min to Yu Gyeong.

1602
01:36:07,480 --> 01:36:08,940
- It's Yu Gyeong.
- Yes.

1603
01:36:08,940 --> 01:36:10,420
What about Min Ju?

1604
01:36:10,420 --> 01:36:12,530
- Seong Min, again.
- Without a doubt.

1605
01:36:12,530 --> 01:36:15,010
It's a waste of time to even discuss it.

1606
01:36:15,010 --> 01:36:17,940
- So Yun still likes Seo Won, right?
- Yes.

1607
01:36:17,940 --> 01:36:20,460
It was so obvious at the bowling alley.

1608
01:36:20,460 --> 01:36:22,290
So Yun to Seo Won.

1609
01:36:22,290 --> 01:36:25,760
But I can't read Seo Won.

1610
01:36:25,760 --> 01:36:28,640
- Seo Won likes Gyu Ri.
- Seo Won likes Gyu Ri.

1611
01:36:28,640 --> 01:36:31,930
- Seo Won never sways.
- It's obvious.

1612
01:36:31,930 --> 01:36:36,170
For Seo Won to ask
if 70-80% is insignificant...

1613
01:36:36,170 --> 01:36:38,190
Jun Hyeon is pretty clear, too, right?

1614
01:36:38,190 --> 01:36:40,200
Jun Hyeon likes Yu Gyeong.

1615
01:36:40,200 --> 01:36:43,040
Jun Hyeon is also the
secret winner of the truth game.

1616
01:36:43,040 --> 01:36:45,480
One more addition for Yu Gyeong.

1617
01:36:45,480 --> 01:36:46,700
He made it.

1618
01:36:46,700 --> 01:36:49,920
Wu Yeol and Jun Hyeon.

1619
01:36:49,920 --> 01:36:52,270
- This is a chance to infiltrate her heart.
- Exactly.

1620
01:36:52,270 --> 01:36:54,640
Everyone was naming their top two,

1621
01:36:54,640 --> 01:36:58,010
but I liked how Jun Hyeon said
he only liked Yu Gyeong.

1622
01:36:58,010 --> 01:36:59,780
- That was impressive.
- He only liked Yu Gyeong.

1623
01:36:59,780 --> 01:37:03,950
He said he was interested in only one,
so Yu Gyeong would hear.

1624
01:37:03,950 --> 01:37:05,120
- Right.
- Let's go.

1625
01:37:05,120 --> 01:37:06,620
Jun Hyeon to Yu Gyeong.

1626
01:37:06,620 --> 01:37:08,030
Jun Hyeon is easy.

1627
01:37:08,030 --> 01:37:10,230
- Wu Yeol...
- Only Wu Yeol and Gyu Ri remain?

1628
01:37:10,230 --> 01:37:12,450
- It's Yu Gyeong.
- That's only right.

1629
01:37:12,450 --> 01:37:15,810
I'm sorry,
but I think Wu Yeol will ask Gyu Ri.

1630
01:37:15,810 --> 01:37:17,270
I agree.

1631
01:37:17,270 --> 01:37:19,050
Their love line is solid,

1632
01:37:19,050 --> 01:37:22,540
but unexpectedly,
he's easily provoked by Gyu Ri.

1633
01:37:22,540 --> 01:37:24,770
- That makes me very anxious.
- Exactly.

1634
01:37:24,770 --> 01:37:26,830
He wants a showdown on their date tomorrow.

1635
01:37:26,830 --> 01:37:29,290
He must be keeping his word
about the three meetings.

1636
01:37:29,290 --> 01:37:31,790
- Geez.
- It's a date request,

1637
01:37:31,790 --> 01:37:33,500
let's go with Gyu Ri.

1638
01:37:33,500 --> 01:37:34,820
I think it's Yu Gyeong.

1639
01:37:34,820 --> 01:37:37,430
- I wish it could be Yu Gyeong.
- Me, too!

1640
01:37:37,430 --> 01:37:40,520
I think that's true.

1641
01:37:40,520 --> 01:37:42,600
Let's jump to Yu Gyeong.

1642
01:37:42,600 --> 01:37:45,260
- Yu Gyeong will ask Wu Yeol.
- Yu Gyeong for Wu Yeol.

1643
01:37:45,260 --> 01:37:47,160
This one is totally easy.

1644
01:37:47,160 --> 01:37:48,770
It can't be Jun Hyeon, can it?

1645
01:37:48,770 --> 01:37:53,300
No. He made it clear today,
and Yu Gyeong recognized it.

1646
01:37:53,300 --> 01:37:55,930
He asked the question
Yu Gyeong wanted to ask.

1647
01:37:55,930 --> 01:37:58,940
And she saw how he even cared for her
at the end.

1648
01:37:58,940 --> 01:38:01,750
He gave her certainty,
no matter who was listening.

1649
01:38:01,750 --> 01:38:03,180
And he was wavering between those two.

1650
01:38:03,180 --> 01:38:05,730
And Yu Gyeong understood.

1651
01:38:05,730 --> 01:38:07,500
He put her at ease.

1652
01:38:07,500 --> 01:38:09,920
You're right. I'm convinced.

1653
01:38:09,920 --> 01:38:12,560
- Yeah, let's go.
- I think we can move on.

1654
01:38:12,560 --> 01:38:14,790
Now, only Gyu Ri remains.

1655
01:38:14,790 --> 01:38:16,750
In my opinion...

1656
01:38:16,750 --> 01:38:18,290
[So interesting]

1657
01:38:18,290 --> 01:38:21,240
Gyu Ri won't choose Wu Yeol after all this.

1658
01:38:21,240 --> 01:38:23,720
- She'll choose Seo Won.
- I agree!

1659
01:38:23,720 --> 01:38:25,520
Because she needs to
smooth it out with Seo Won.

1660
01:38:25,520 --> 01:38:28,760
Gyu Ri revealed
that she liked Seo Won 70-80%.

1661
01:38:28,760 --> 01:38:31,990
But that conversation became meaningless.

1662
01:38:31,990 --> 01:38:36,350
I think Gyu Ri needs to smooth
it out with Seo Won.

1663
01:38:36,350 --> 01:38:38,830
I think Gyu Ri might choose Wu Yeol.

1664
01:38:38,830 --> 01:38:43,430
But didn't Wu Yeol and Gyu Ri
recently go on a nickname date?

1665
01:38:43,430 --> 01:38:46,440
The way I see it,
Heart Signal will be divided

1666
01:38:46,440 --> 01:38:49,410
into the before-and-after the truth game now.

1667
01:38:49,410 --> 01:38:54,030
Whether or not Gyu Ri provokes
Wu Yeol and chooses someone else,

1668
01:38:54,030 --> 01:38:55,580
it might all end here.

1669
01:38:55,580 --> 01:38:58,980
There might be a showdown
tomorrow since it's a date.

1670
01:38:58,980 --> 01:39:01,190
Judging by Gyu Ri's personality,

1671
01:39:01,190 --> 01:39:03,650
I think she knows that if she doesn't
choose Seo Won this time,

1672
01:39:03,650 --> 01:39:07,490
she knows she'll lose him for good.

1673
01:39:07,490 --> 01:39:10,430
Because when he asked
if 70-80% was insignificant,

1674
01:39:10,430 --> 01:39:12,250
she seemed to wake up.

1675
01:39:12,250 --> 01:39:15,080
She directed many of her comments at Wu Yeol.

1676
01:39:15,080 --> 01:39:18,310
This is why I think she'll choose
Seo Won this time.

1677
01:39:18,310 --> 01:39:20,680
- Let's choose Seo Won.
- Gyu Ri to Seo Won.

1678
01:39:20,680 --> 01:39:23,730
Gyu Ri to Seo Won does make sense.

1679
01:39:23,730 --> 01:39:25,600
All done! We're done.

1680
01:39:25,600 --> 01:39:29,240
I'm not too sure about Min Ju today.

1681
01:39:29,240 --> 01:39:32,480
I don't think it's Seong Min,
but I can't say for sure who it is.

1682
01:39:32,480 --> 01:39:35,110
It's either Seong Min or Jun Hyeon.

1683
01:39:35,110 --> 01:39:37,550
She got to know Seong Min,

1684
01:39:37,550 --> 01:39:40,010
so don't you think
she'll go out with Jun Hyeon?

1685
01:39:40,010 --> 01:39:44,860
So, Min Ju was disappointed in
Seong Min's approach to the truth game.

1686
01:39:44,860 --> 01:39:47,060
He shouldn't have said what he said.

1687
01:39:47,060 --> 01:39:50,900
- So, you think Min Ju changed?
- Min Ju to Jun Hyeon.

1688
01:39:50,900 --> 01:39:53,100
Good job, Min Ju. Good riddance!

1689
01:39:53,100 --> 01:39:56,750
Please let us be right.
I'd be so happy if that happened.

1690
01:39:56,750 --> 01:39:59,800
Okay, Seo Won's choice is...

1691
01:40:01,050 --> 01:40:04,900
[Went on a date with Gyu Ri]

1692
01:40:04,900 --> 01:40:08,130
[So Yun confessed her feelings for Seo Won]

1693
01:40:09,240 --> 01:40:10,640
[Seo Won to Gyu Ri]

1694
01:40:10,640 --> 01:40:12,290
We were right.

1695
01:40:12,290 --> 01:40:14,820
And Gyu Ri's choice?

1696
01:40:16,230 --> 01:40:18,420
[The galbijjim was for Wu Yeol]

1697
01:40:18,420 --> 01:40:20,360
[Seo Won was her first choice]

1698
01:40:21,470 --> 01:40:23,430
[Gyu Ri to Seo Won]

1699
01:40:23,430 --> 01:40:24,905
She needs to smooth it out with Seo Won.

1700
01:40:24,905 --> 01:40:26,805
So Yun's choice is?

1701
01:40:27,590 --> 01:40:31,190
[Straight ahead for Seo Won?]

1702
01:40:32,296 --> 01:40:33,400
[So Yun to Seo Won]

1703
01:40:33,400 --> 01:40:36,915
That's right! Write a new story with Seo Won.

1704
01:40:36,915 --> 01:40:39,105
Seong Min's choice is?

1705
01:40:40,040 --> 01:40:44,040
[Yu Gyeong vs. Min Ju,
who will Seong Min choose?]

1706
01:40:45,185 --> 01:40:47,230
[Seong Min to Yu Gyeong]

1707
01:40:47,230 --> 01:40:49,125
He should just get this tattooed.

1708
01:40:49,125 --> 01:40:51,225
Jun Hyeon's choice is?

1709
01:40:53,340 --> 01:40:56,640
[Yu Gyeong, the only one in his heart?]

1710
01:40:57,705 --> 01:40:58,561
[Jun Hyeon to Yu Gyeong]

1711
01:40:58,561 --> 01:41:01,225
Yes! This is the perfect timing.

1712
01:41:01,225 --> 01:41:03,355
Min Ju's choice is?

1713
01:41:04,360 --> 01:41:10,340
[Straight ahead for Seong Min again?]

1714
01:41:12,210 --> 01:41:15,560
[Min Ju to Jun Hyeon]

1715
01:41:15,560 --> 01:41:16,640
Min Ju...

1716
01:41:16,640 --> 01:41:18,900
That's right!

1717
01:41:18,900 --> 01:41:21,540
Turn on the World Cup song.

1718
01:41:21,540 --> 01:41:23,900
I'm so happy Min Ju changed her mind.

1719
01:41:23,900 --> 01:41:26,290
I think Min Ju made the wise choice.

1720
01:41:26,290 --> 01:41:27,900
It took her long enough.

1721
01:41:27,900 --> 01:41:29,960
Yu Gyeong's choice is?

1722
01:41:29,960 --> 01:41:31,380
Yu Gyeong...

1723
01:41:31,380 --> 01:41:36,030
[Jun Hyeon's simple
but unmistakable feelings]

1724
01:41:36,030 --> 01:41:39,880
[Wu Yeol, who always expressed how he felt?]

1725
01:41:41,020 --> 01:41:42,900
[Yu Gyeong to Wu Yeol]

1726
01:41:42,900 --> 01:41:45,490
- Yes.
- She needs to reprimand him.

1727
01:41:45,490 --> 01:41:48,900
- Wu Yeol's choice is?
- Wu Yeol...

1728
01:41:48,900 --> 01:41:54,080
[Gyu Ri or Yu Gyeong?]

1729
01:41:57,080 --> 01:41:59,970
[Wu Yeol to Gyu Ri]

1730
01:41:59,970 --> 01:42:01,400
[Shocked]

1731
01:42:01,400 --> 01:42:03,580
- Is he nuts?
- Gyu Ri?

1732
01:42:03,580 --> 01:42:05,570
[Chaotic]

1733
01:42:05,570 --> 01:42:07,970
[What's going on?]

1734
01:42:07,970 --> 01:42:10,050
Wu Yeol, let's not meet for another week.

1735
01:42:10,050 --> 01:42:13,890
And with that, the prediction panel's
date selection guesses

1736
01:42:13,890 --> 01:42:15,700
were a success!

1737
01:42:15,700 --> 01:42:17,680
This day has really come.

1738
01:42:17,680 --> 01:42:19,660
I really couldn't see this coming.

1739
01:42:19,660 --> 01:42:24,320
The storm brought on a tsunami.
What happened?

1740
01:42:24,320 --> 01:42:27,900
I had said I think I should meet
someone at least three times.

1741
01:42:27,900 --> 01:42:31,950
Shouldn't you feel bad toward me?

1742
01:42:31,950 --> 01:42:36,700
You've already slipped
through my fingers, huh?

1743
01:42:36,700 --> 01:42:38,870
Yes. Wait, let's talk.

1744
01:42:38,870 --> 01:42:40,950
I think I regretted it.

1745
01:42:40,950 --> 01:42:45,450
I think she took up a big part
of my heart at some point.

1746
01:42:45,450 --> 01:42:47,990
I wanted to turn everything back.

1747
01:42:49,930 --> 01:42:52,990
They say love is timing.

1748
01:42:52,990 --> 01:42:54,770
- Are you okay?
- Yeah.

1749
01:42:54,770 --> 01:42:57,960
The more I talk to Jun Hyeon...

1750
01:42:57,960 --> 01:43:01,760
I'm not curious about anyone else, but you.

1751
01:43:01,760 --> 01:43:03,980
My feelings are growing.

1752
01:43:05,190 --> 01:43:07,500
There's no one but you.

1753
01:43:07,500 --> 01:43:09,270
Who did you choose?

1754
01:43:09,270 --> 01:43:10,490
Is it obvious?

1755
01:43:10,490 --> 01:43:12,600
Gosh, seriously...

1756
01:43:12,600 --> 01:43:13,760
I'm going crazy.

1757
01:43:13,760 --> 01:43:17,720
It was the first time I was drawn to
someone I didn't expect to be at all.

1758
01:43:17,720 --> 01:43:20,440
They're like a married couple
after today's date.

1759
01:43:20,440 --> 01:43:22,060
Today is my only chance.

1760
01:43:22,060 --> 01:43:25,030
I didn't want to meet you.

1761
01:43:25,030 --> 01:43:26,730
That woke me up.

1762
01:43:27,940 --> 01:43:30,641
I felt I should give her a clear answer.

1763
01:43:30,641 --> 01:43:37,421
How would you feel
if I sent you a text today?

1764
01:43:38,275 --> 01:43:41,450
"That's how you roll? This is how I roll."

1765
01:43:41,450 --> 01:43:43,480
And I'd let you go.

1766
01:43:44,900 --> 01:43:52,000
I realized my feelings for Yu Gyeong
were very strong.
